# M6 slipstream-trap-fix — verify no chassis can wedge anywhere on
# slipstream's basement_ceil or catwalk surfaces. Spawns Heavy at the
# basement_ceil edge near the (now removed) right slide chute and
# walks back-and-forth across what used to be the trap zone.

window 1280 720
seed 1 0
out build/shots/m6_slipstream_no_trap
map slipstream
no_parallax
loadout heavy "Microgun" "Burst SMG" Light Standard

# basement_ceil top y=1216 → spawn pelvis 40 above = 1176.
# x=2200 (tile 68.75) was deep inside the right chute interior pre-fix.
spawn_at 2200 1176

at 5   shot stand_t005

# Walk left across former chute zone (cols 64-72 = x=2048-2304).
at 30  press left
at 60  shot walk_left_t060
at 120 shot walk_left_t120
at 180 shot walk_left_t180
at 240 shot walk_left_t240
at 300 release left

# Walk right back across.
at 320 press right
at 380 shot walk_right_t380
at 440 shot walk_right_t440
at 500 shot walk_right_t500
at 560 shot walk_right_t560
at 600 release right

contact_sheet trap_sheet cols 5 cell 320 180

at 660 end
